ISLAMABAD, Feb 15 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi and Begum Samina Alvi Tuesday visited the residence of Minister for Maritime Affairs Syed Ali Haider Zaidi to condole over the demise of his father.
The president prayed for peace of the departed soul and strength to the bereaved family to bear the loss.
